						</label>
						<label class="checkbox">
					</div>
				</div>`;

  			}
			else if (radio_input === 'stage'){
				result.innerHTML = `<div class="mb-2 mr-2 has-text-weight-bold">Choose one, both or neither. If neither are selected then the result will be for BOTH STAGES.</div>
